    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The functions in this group are similar to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/accelerate/1450226-vdsp_vrampmul"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", but rather than overwriting the output vector, they add the results to the existing values in the output vector. The following code describes the calculation:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeListing",
          "code": [
            "for (i = 0; i < N; ++i) {",
            "    O[i*OS] += *Start * I[i*IS];",
            "    *Start += *Step;",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "other",
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "3239855",
            "title": "Listing 1"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For example, the following code fills the array "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "i"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " with sine values:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeListing",
          "code": [
            "let n = vDSP_Length(1024)",
            "",
            "let i: [Float] = (0 ..< n).map {",
            "    return sin(Float($0) / 20)",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "3239808",
            "title": "Listing 2"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The following illustrates the values of "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "i"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ":"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "image",
              "identifier": "media-3239803",
              "metadata": {
                "anchor": "3239803",
                "title": "Figure 1"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The following code fills the output array, o, with increasing powers of two:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeListing",
          "code": [
            "var o = (0 ..< n).map {",
            "    return pow(Float($0), 2) * 0.0001",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "3239832",
            "title": "Listing 3"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The following illustrates the values of "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "o"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ":"
